          <li>Fix an issue with wired connections repeatedly reconnecting</li>
          <li>Updated translations</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="2.4.1" date="2021-09-08" urgency="medium">
      <description>
        <p>Minor updates</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Fix a crash on startup for some devices</li>
          <li>Updated translations</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="2.4.0" date="2021-07-14" urgency="medium">
      <description>
        <p>Minor updates</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Show message when Ethernet is unplugged</li>
          <li>Show DNS info</li>
          <li>Updated translations</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="2.3.3" date="2020-10-08" urgency="medium">
      <description>
        <p>Minor updates</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Better status when wireless network is disabled</li>
          <li>Updated translations</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="2.3.2" date="2020-09-02" urgency="medium">
      <description>
